@startuml
' Visão compacta: poucas setas, leitura por camadas.
' Detalhe por ficheiro: architecture.puml ou architecture-theme-*.puml
' Ver docs/architecture-diagrams.md
!theme plain
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam roundcorner 8
skinparam ArrowThickness 1.2
skinparam linetype ortho

title plantuml-plugin-manorfm v0.11.14 — camadas (visão leitura)

top to bottom direction

together {
  package "Composição" as P1 #EEF6EE {
    component [extension.ts] as EXT <<entry>>
  }
  package "Partilhado" as P2 #E8ECF4 {
    component [config + registo + util] as SHARED <<abstract>>
  }
}

package "Funcionalidades (UI)" as P_UI #F4F0E8 {
  component [barra, code lens, formatação] as UI <<abstract>>
}

package "Apresentação" as P4 #F8ECEC {
  component [custom editor + preview Webview] as VIEW <<abstract>>
}

package "Domínio PlantUML" as P5 #EEEEEE {
  component [HTTP + texto + render + export] as DOM <<abstract>>
}

cloud "Servidor PlantUML (HTTP)" as SRV #LightBlue

EXT -down-> SHARED : lê / invalida
EXT -down-> UI : regista
EXT -down-> VIEW : regista
EXT -down-> DOM : comandos export

UI -down-> SHARED
VIEW -down-> SHARED
VIEW -down-> DOM : pipeline, fetch, includes
DOM -down-> SHARED : tipos / sessão\n(via módulos)
DOM -down-> SRV

legend bottom
  **Abstract** = vários ficheiros; nomes exactos em **architecture.puml**.
  **Não** há ciclo RP↔SC: só **renderPipeline** importa **serverClient** (unidireccional).
  **Partilhado** inclui **plantumlEditorSessionRegistry** (documento activo sem provider).
endlegend

@enduml
